  The A Wizard is Never Lates and the Simbelmynes allow you to dig out characters and weapons. The Hearken to Me is used with the Rider&#39;s Spear to act like Theoden&#39;s Sword, but for one less. Gamling gives you an excuse to play your possessions during the skirmish phase.<br />
SHADOW<br />
